	(text_box "Especificaciones:\nTypical Application\n8.2.1 TPS54302 8-V to 28-V Input, 5-V Output Converter\nInput voltage range = 8 Vto 28 V\nOutput voltage = 5 V\nOutput current = 3 A\nTransient response, 1.5-A load step = ΔVOUT = ±5 %\nInput ripple voltage = 400 mV\nOutput voltage ripple = 30 mVpp\nSwitching frequency = 400 kHz\n\nCapacitores X7R"
